  14,5,"Indeed, We sent Moses with Our signs, ňĻordering him,ňļ ‚ÄúLead your people out of darkness and into light, and remind them of God‚Äôs days ňĻof favourňļ.‚ÄĚ Surely in this are signs for whoever is steadfast, grateful"
